title.narrative: Rural Development: Sustainable Rural Development for the Poor Project in Ha Tinh and Quang Binh Provinces

description.narrative: The goal of the project shall be to sustainably improve income and reduce vulnerability of rural poor households in targeted upland land areas of Ha Tinh and Quang Binh provinces The objective of the project shall be to invest in climate smart, socially equitable and profitable rural development models that promote pro-poor market linkages, value chains and enhanced rural business competitiveness
